<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Features - Health Food Checker</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial;
        }

        .features-page {
            padding: 60px 0;
        }

        .features-page h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .features-page .step {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .features-page .step h2 {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .features-page .step p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .features-page .step img {
            width:60px;
            height: auto;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .step-number {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #007bff;
        }

        .auth-section {
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .auth-section h2 {
            font-size: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .auth-section .auth-description {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    
    <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>
    

    <div class="features-page container">
        <h1>How It Works</h1>
        <div class="row">
    
            <div class="col-md-6 step">
                <span class="step-number">1. Data Input</span>
                <h2>Entering Your Information</h2>
                <p>Start by entering your personal details such as height and weight. This information is crucial for accurate calculations and recommendations.</p>
                <img src="/images/personal.png" alt="Data Input">
            </div>
        
            <div class="col-md-6 step">
                <span class="step-number">2. BMI Calculation</span>
                <h2>Calculating Your BMI</h2>
                <p>Based on the information provided, we calculate your Body Mass Index (BMI). This value helps determine your current weight status and compares with previous readings that lets you track improvements over time.</p>
                <img src="/images/weighing.jpg" alt="BMI Calculation">
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 step">
                <span class="step-number">3. Nutritional Analysis</span>
                <h2>Analyzing Your Food Intake</h2>
                <p>Log the food items you consume daily. We analyze these entries to provide insights into your nutritional intake and identify areas for improvement.</p>
                <img src="/images/analysis.jpg" alt="Nutritional Analysis">
            </div>
    
            <div class="col-md-6 step">
                <span class="step-number">4. Personalized Recommendations</span>
                <h2>Receiving Tailored Recommendations</h2>
                <p>Based on your nutritional analysis, we provide suggestions to help you make healthier choices and achieve your wellness goals.</p>
                <img src="/images/recommend.png" alt="Personalized Recommendations">
            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="auth-section">
            <h2>Create Your Account and Login</h2>
            <div class="auth-description">
                <p><strong>Create Account:</strong> To get started, you need to create an account. Click on the "Create Account" button and fill in the required details such as your name, email address, and password. This will allow you to save your personal information securely and confidentially while tracking your progress over time.</p>
                <p><strong>Login:</strong> If you already have an account, simply click on the "Login" button. Enter your registered username and password to access your account. Once logged in, you can view your personalized recommendations and track your nutritional intake.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
